Package org.jscsi.exception

This package contains all exceptions, which can occur by this iSCSI (RFC 3720) implementation.

See:
          Description

Exception Summary
ConfigurationException Exception for handling exception occuring while configuration setup.
InternetSCSIException This is a base class for the exception handling at the parsing process of the iSCSI protocol.
NoSuchConnectionException NoSuchConnectionException

This exception is thrown when no connection is open.
NoSuchSessionException NoSuchSessionException

This exception is thrown when no session is open.
OperationalTextKeyException OperationalTextKeyException

This exception is thrown when an error with an OperationalTextKey occurs.
TaskExecutionException Handling exceptions occuring while executing any kind of multithreaded task.
 

Package org.jscsi.exception Description

This package contains all exceptions, which can occur by this iSCSI (RFC 3720) implementation.
